data.title: 2008) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Only date was 29 May 1935 inscription- 'Rest in Peace'. Buried beside- Bonnie Lawhun Grant Doyle Walls, 73, of Roanoke VA, formerly of Logan County, went home to be with the Lord on Wednesday, November 5, 2008, from Roanoke.
